        "salary": "",
        "description": "<div class=\"h3\">Company Description</div>\n<p>ClientSolv Technologies is an IT solution firm with over a decade of experience serving Fortune 1000 companies, public sector and small to medium sized companies. ClientSolv Technologies is a woman-owned and operated company that is certified as a WMBE, 8a firm by the Federal government's Small Business Administration.</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Job Description</div>\n<p>We are seeking a QA Test Engineer with automation experience for a direct-hire/permanent  role supporting an outcome-focused workflow optimization platform.  This role will be fully remote and will offer a salary and a comprehensive benefit package.  </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>In this role, you will be responsible for: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Automate acceptance testing methods</li>\n<li>Collaborate closely with our Product Managers, Designers, and Developers to understand the requirements, acceptance criteria, and how the software is supposed to perform</li>\n<li>You will select and deploy automation tools, and continuously add more test cases with each sprint</li>\n<li>Ensuring solution supports the stories being produced by the Product Managers</li>\n<li>Manually testing releases until automation is in place</li>\n<li>Help determine root cause and how to reproduce bugs based on reported symptoms</li>\n<li>Recommending and deploying automation to replace the manual testing</li>\n<li>Determining priority for test scenarios</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Qualifications</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience establishing an automated test environment from scratch</li>\n<li>5+ years in a software QA role</li>\n<li>3+ years of experience leveraging automated test tools for web-based SaaS products</li>\n<li>Understand available QA automation solutions with ability to match the right tool for our needs</li>\n<li>Appropriate programming skills to script automation</li>\n<li>Experience testing applications with responsive and adaptive design with a “mobile first” approach</li>\n<li>Creative problem-solving skills</li>\n<li>History of delivering projects on time</li>\n<li>Experience working in a fully Agile environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nice to have…</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Successful track record working with remote team members</li>\n<li>Background in financial services technology</li>\n<li>Azure DevOps</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Additional Information</div>\n<p><strong>This direct hire/permanent role will be a remote role and will offer a salary plus benefits, such as </strong><strong>Medical/Dental/Vision premiums covered at 100% for the employee and 50% for additional members of your family and unlimited paid time off.</strong></p>\n"
