        "description": "<p><em>Do you want to get involved with your skills and your personality and become part of a success story?</em></p>\n<p><em>Are you looking for a team in which you can exchange openly and directly, support and challenge each other?</em></p>\n<p><em>Join <a href=\"https://www.aheadintranet.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ahead</a>'s remote team and take an active role in shaping the future of our platform!</em></p>\n<p>As a spin-off of isolutions, our mission at <a href=\"https://www.aheadintranet.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ahead </a>is to create an intranet platform that paves the way towards modern internal communication. We help companies to connect with their workforce across different locations and give them a tool to easily put into action their communication strategy and easily build a knowledgebase for their teams.</p>\n<p>We focus on building a secure, fast, and robust platform that enables our customers to have a digital communication channel directly from the cloud.</p>\n<p>Collaborating with a dynamic team of experienced architects and developers, that works along the needs of our customers, you will be involved in the entire product design process. Your skills will be keys for maintaining a high level of quality and create a pleasant and bug-free experience for our users.</p>\n<p>We have already iterated a few years on requirements analysis, design, architecture, development, and testing, but that does not mean that we think that we know it all.</p>\n<p>Every change that brings us closer to only working on things with a high impact is warmly welcome!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.aheadintranet.com/company/about-us\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Meet the Team</strong></a></p>\n<div class=\"h3\"><strong>Your profile</strong></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of the Microsoft Azure platform and web technologies like C#, ASP.NET Core (at least 2 years of experience).</li>\n<li>You love to improve and automate methodology and processes.</li>\n<li>You have a flair for quality and testing.</li>\n<li>You focus on quality and work in a structured and methodical way.</li>\n<li>Completed university degree in Computer Science or equivalent professional training.</li>\n<li>Fluent level of English to communicate in an international team.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"h4\">Nice to have</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience in software product development within the SaaS environment.</li>\n<li>experience in React and TypeScript.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If your experience looks a little different from what we've identified and you think you can add value to our crew, we'd love to learn more about you.</p>\n<div class=\"h3\"><strong>You can expect</strong></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Being part of a successful and agile team that drives product development and innovation with a lot of drive and entrepreneurship. </li>\n<li>You will be actively taking part in the development of the product and be involved in the entire design process: requirements analysis, design, architecture, development, and testing. </li>\n<li>Work and evolve with the latest technologies like .NET Core, C#, Azure, Cosmos DB, Azure Search, Event grid, Influx DB, etc; </li>\n<li>Continuously improve your skills thanks to a yearly training budget.</li>\n<li>Choose your own hardware. </li>\n<li>Remote working and flexible working-hour. (If you are based in Barcelona, you can enjoy our office near Urquinaona); </li>\n<li>One additional week of vacation for Corporate Social Responsibility. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><br>Are a passionate and forward-thinking person with the desire to build a great product?</p>\n<p>Apply now and let yourself be infected by our unique StartUp-Spirit!<br><br> You can find out more about us at  <a href=\"http://www.aheadintranet.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">aheadintranet.com</a>.</p>\n"
