        "description": "<div class=\"h3\">Company Description</div>\n<p>Perry Street Software is Jack’d and SCRUFF. We are two of the world’s largest gay, bi, trans and queer social dating apps on iOS and Android. Our brands reach more than 20 million members worldwide so members can connect, meet and express themselves on a platform that prioritizes privacy, security, and community.</p>\n<p><strong>Perry Street employees receive the best perks out there – great benefits including a 401k plan with employer match, comprehensive healthcare coverage</strong>,<strong> paid parental leave, fully remote options</strong><strong> and a flexible vacation policy.</strong> </p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Job Description</div>\n<p>We are hiring experienced Android developers to help us build the next-generation version of Scruff and Jack’d. We are a small, agile, nimble company, so the ability to make an impact is significant. The position is permanent and full-time.</p>\n<p><strong>What you'll do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Develop with the latest technologies in evolving the architecture for current and future needs in order to develop innovative, consumer-facing mobile products, while supporting the product roadmap</li>\n<li>Work in an agile team with Product, Design, Support, and Marketing to respond to our users needs</li>\n<li>Help develop solutions end to end, from the design, to requirements, coding, refactoring, delivering, and maintenance</li>\n<li>Be a good communicator with both a local and remote team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Qualifications</div>\n<p><strong>Who you are:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bachelor’s degree (or higher) in computer science, related field, or equivalent practical experience</li>\n<li>3+ years of software development experience</li>\n<li>1+ year of Android app development experience</li>\n<li>Experience using design and architecture patterns</li>\n<li>Strong knowledge of Java &amp; Kotlin with the Android SDK</li>\n<li>Experience using RxJava</li>\n<li>Good sense of usability and product for mobile apps</li>\n<li>Strong sense of ownership, ability to work independently, and proven track record of driving products</li>\n<li>Shipped consumer Android apps, ideally available on Google Play</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Nice to Have:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience with Swift</li>\n<li>Full stack knowledge of technologies like Ruby, SQL, Linux, React Native, and AWS would be highly desirable</li>\n<li>Experience with advanced animations</li>\n<li>Experience with MVVM architectures and Android Architecture Components</li>\n<li>Data-driven mindset</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Additional Information</div>\n<p>Perry Street is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer. We do not discriminate based upon race, religion, color, gender, gender identity or expression, sexual orientation, genetic information, national origin, ancestry, medical condition, disability, marital status, caregiver status, pregnancy, citizenship, age, military or veteran status, or other applicable legally protected characteristics.</p>\n<p>All your information will be kept confidential according to EEO guidelines.</p>\n"
