        "_id": "613f8897c1c0b3646447b316",
        "url": "https://remotive.io/remote-jobs/software-dev/senior-fullstack-developer-m-f-d-858392",
        "title": "Senior FullStack Developer (m/f/d)",
        "company_name": "Sastrify",
        "category": "Software Development",
        "job_type": "full_time",
        "publication_date": "2021-08-25T05:42:18.000Z",
        "candidate_required_location": "Between CET-1 and CET+1",
        "salary": "",
        "description": "<p>Sastrify supports Tech, Finance and Procurement teams in buying and renewing SaaS subscriptions so they can focus on what matters while we save their time and money by applying best practices in SaaS buying and using a dedicated procurement team that benefits from a large database of benchmarks.</p>\n<p><strong>Join us on our new adventure to reshape the software-as-a-service industry!</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Role</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Our teams are cross-functional, self-organised and autonomous</li>\n<li>Collaboration is part of our DNA: the whole team is responsible to come up with solutions to solve customer problems in the most effective and efficient manner</li>\n<li>This approach requires a big amount of communication, teamwork and maturity We strongly believe it’s the best way to create software</li>\n<li>As a Senior Developer you apply all your skills, share your experience and mentor your teammates</li>\n<li>You are involved in the whole application lifecycle, in architecture and in DevOps</li>\n<li>You focus on getting high-quality, reusable and tested code into production</li>\n<li>You promote a culture of agility and excellence, where writing automated tests and applying best practices and industry standards are an everyday habit</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Our Technologies</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>We write our products with TypeScript: React.js in the Front- and Node.js in the Back-End</li>\n<li>Our serverless architecture runs on AWS Lambdas</li>\n<li>We have fully automated CI/CD pipelines with automated tests and linting</li>\n<li>Further technologies include: Serverless Framework, PostgreSQL, TypeORM and React Query</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>You are an experienced FullStack JavaScript expert with at least 7 years of software development experience</li>\n<li>You love to code and deliver high quality products into production</li>\n<li>For you it's normal to be involved in the whole software development lifecycle, not just coding down some requirements</li>\n<li>You are passionate about collaboration and being part of a team</li>\n<li>You are a good communicator who enjoys discussing problems and solutions with others</li>\n<li>You believe in continuous learning and improvement and consider mistakes part of achieving great results</li>\n<li>You are fluent in English and keen to work remotely (we don't have an office)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Full responsibility from day one</li>\n<li>Work with our amazing international team</li>\n<li>30 vacation days</li>\n<li>Your personal learning budget</li>\n<li>Remote-first mindset (you can work from anywhere between CET-1 and CET+1)</li>\n</ul>\n"
