        "description": "<p>Equisolve is seeking a talented, motivated senior Web developer ready to develop new websites and applications and help guide our team of developers.</p>\n<p>As the team lead, you will lead a team of web developers developers building websites and web applications for our clients.</p>\n<p>You will be integral in setting and documenting code standards and ensuring quality and security in the code you write and review.</p>\n<p>This position requires senior-level technical ability, clear communication, excellent leadership skills.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"h3\">What You'll Be Doing</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Leading a team of web developers writing PHP, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</li>\n<li>Identifying technical requirements for websites and applications</li>\n<li>Working with the Design and UX team to ensure you have what you need to meet project requirements</li>\n<li>Writing secure, performant and accessible code</li>\n<li>Reviewing and providing feedback on code written by your team, ensuring high performance and security</li>\n<li>Documenting processes and best practices</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You will have a team of developers available to assist you in your growth at Equisolve as you get up to speed.</p>\n<p>This is a remote position, but you do need to be mostly available during US Eastern Time Zone hours.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"h3\">The Tools You’ll Use</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Our PHP-based content management system</li>\n<li>CMS framework and vanilla PHP for templating and development</li>\n<li>SASS for styles</li>\n<li>Github for versioning and code reviews</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"h3\"> </div>\n<div class=\"h3\">About You</div>\n<ul>\n<li>You've successfully led a team of developers in a fast-paced, demanding environment</li>\n<li>You've built websites, applications or features from the ground up using PHP or another server-side, object-oriented programing language</li>\n<li>You've worked in a CMS creating custom templates and functionality and written extensions or plugins</li>\n<li>You have a deep understanding of object-oriented programming–enough to write and review code, documentation and standards</li>\n<li>You're knowledgeable on front-end and server-side security best-practices</li>\n<li>You pay attention to the details and make sure you've hit on all requirements for a task or project</li>\n<li>You like the idea of a fast-paced work environment and the opportunity to touch a lot of different types of projects and code</li>\n<li>You're comfortable talking with your co-workers and clients alike. You know how to craft the right response for the right reaction and aren't afraid to pick up the phone if you have to.</li>\n<li>You've worked from home before or have a plan for success for your first work-from-home position</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We are only set up for US employees so you must be in the US and legally able to work here.</p>\n<div class=\"h3\"> </div>\n<div class=\"h3\">Nice to Have</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Working knowledge of WCAG 2.1 AA standards</li>\n<li>Familiarity with JavaScript MVVMs like Vue or React</li>\n<li>Comfortable working with Git</li>\n<li>ADA Compliance Certified a HUGE plus!</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"h3\"> </div>\n<div class=\"h3\">About Equisolve</div>\n<p>Equisolve is an award-winning digital agency providing website development and ongoing website management services to public companies. Equisolve is based in Palm City, FL with a remote team spread throughout the US.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Experience writing secure, performant and accessible code</li>\n<li>Knowledge of PHP, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><strong>There is a quick code test at the end of this application. Please complete!</strong> <br>If your resume is selected, more in-depth assessments as part of our application process will be requested.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Work from home with an A+ team in a casual work environment</li>\n<li>Medical, dental and long-term disability insurance</li>\n<li>Continuing education, training and support</li>\n<li>Generous PTO and sick time</li>\n<li>Work with the latest technology</li>\n<li>All equipment will be provided to you.</li>\n</ul>\n"
