        "description": "<div><strong>Do you want to be part of an innovative and disruptive company? This challenge is for you! </strong></div>\n<div>We are looking for an <strong>Engineering Manager</strong> who wants to join a growing startup that is hitting in his sector: Landbot!</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">First things first... top project details!</strong></div>\n<div><strong>- Company/team</strong></div>\n<div>Landbot is the <strong>no-code chatbot builder that helps marketing teams assist customers</strong> at scale. They are helping <strong>+<a class=\"postings-link\" href=\"http://50.0.0.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\">50.000</a> businesses creating conversational experiences</strong>, WOW! In your day-to-day, you will work in squads and in the most agile way together with the Senior Product Manager, Product Designer, Data, Frontend, and Backend Developers.</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong>- Values</strong> </div>\n<div>With operations in more than <strong>40 countries</strong>, <strong>Landbot is a start-up </strong>that offers a platform that helps companies create unbeatable chatbot conversations on different channels: Web, WhatsApp, and Messenger</div>\n<div>If the values <strong>Human-First, Adaptability, and Unity fit </strong>the project you are looking for, here the search is over!</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong>- Day to day</strong> </div>\n<div><strong>Transparency, motivation, enthusiasm, and creativity, passion for continuous learning</strong>, startup defines you ... It is the ideal place for you. In order to automate business processes for non-technical users in the easiest and most agile way in the market, Landbot is constantly expanding.</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Your mission 🚀</strong></div>\n<div>In your day-to-day life, you should establish clear OKRs, carry out 1: 1 weekly and provide regular comments to team members (between 4 - 7). You will have the possibility to Recruit and expand your team when necessary.</div>\n<div>Be a team coach, helping them advance in their own career.</div>\n<div>Collaboration within a cross-functional product and design team to build your team's long-term vision and strategy will also be part of your mission.</div>\n<div>Great if you have experience training your team to achieve a high level of excellence and quality. Create simple and scalable technical solutions.</div>\n<div>Empathy will be your main tool.</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Perks, my friend!</strong></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>A competitive salary package and working in a company of continuous growth and expansion. Career projection is always present!</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>Great culture and work environment, young and international atmosphere.</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>Live and work in sunny Barcelona if you love the beach is your place (if your choice is working onsite)</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>Friday happy hours after our weekly team meetings.</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>Open vacation policy and flexible holidays, so you can take time off when you need it.</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>Extra transportation tickets, educational content, and everything you need to feel empowered.</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>If you bring someone as talented as you there is a prize!</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>First-class work team.</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">✔ </span>Open Salary range according to your experience. First, know you and then you'll talk about what are you looking for!</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">If this is you – holy cow! 🐄</strong></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">• </span>You have at least <strong>3-5 years of experience in a similar position.</strong></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">•</span> The <strong>empathetic, curious, inclusive, and proactive attitude are some of your best soft skills.</strong></div>\n<div>• One of your passions is being able to make a great impact on people through technology.</div>\n<div>• You have worked in engineering leadership, coaching, and mentoring roles.</div>\n<div>• Amazing if you have excellent <strong>problem-solving skills.</strong></div>\n<div>• Ability to see the big picture and guide the team to design a scalable architecture.</div>\n<div>• Experience with the cloud platforms.</div>\n<div>• Great if you have<strong> knowledge of JS, Node JS, or Python.</strong></div>\n<div>• <strong>Speak English and Spanish fluently (essential).</strong></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong style=\"font-size: 24px;\">If this is also you – JACKPOT! 🍒🍒🍒</strong></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">•</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"> </span>Eligibility to work in Spain</strong></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">• </span>You work or have worked in a startup and you love it!</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">• </span>If the word that best defines you would be proactivity. It is you, my friend. We want tirelessly resourceful people on board!</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div><strong>Let’s have a chat and GetWith us! 😊</strong></div>\n"
