        "description": "<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Description de l'entreprise</div>\n<p>Nous avons été fondés en septembre 2018, il y a 2 ans, par Alexandre Dardy (ex McKinsey et Co-fondateur de Lazada, vendu pour 3,2Mds$ à Alibaba après 6 ans) et Mehdi Tahri (ex McKinsey, Amazon).</p>\n<p>En 18 mois, nous sommes devenus la première plateforme numérique d'intérim en France, avec +800 000 intérimaires disponibles, au service de 2000 clients et doublant le chiffre d'affaires tous les 2 mois !</p>\n<p>Nous sommes aujourd'hui 220 personnes, toutes passionnées avec un fort esprit entrepreneurial, un important réseau de 120 partners et avons récemment levé 35 millions d'euros qui vont nous permettre de nous développer encore plus, en France et à l'international (Bureau à Milan ouvert en novembre 2020).</p>\n<p>Nous avons un objectif significatif et ambitieux : redéfinir le marché du travail temporaire (marché de 150 Mds€ en Europe) avec un modèle de marketplace évolutif centré sur le travailleur.</p>\n<p>Notre mission : Utiliser la technologie pour améliorer radicalement l'accès aux emplois et à l'expérience professionnelle pour tous.</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Description du poste</div>\n<p>As you might understand, the technical part is very important because it is at the core of our growth and our ambitions.</p>\n<p><strong>The stack you'll work on 🛠 : </strong></p>\n<p>* Language : Swift<br>* Architecture: MVVM<br>* Tools : RxSwift / Parse<br>* CI/CD : Fastlane / Circle CI / Browserstack</p>\n<p>You do not have to master all these tools but you are willing to learn them.<br>The hypergrowth of our company requires you to be ready to face the expansion of your scope and platform. </p>\n<p><strong>What we can offer you:</strong></p>\n<p>An unforgettable experience!</p>\n<p>Your work will have an impact. You will be counted on. What you develop will matter and make an immediate difference to your users.</p>\n<p>The opportunity to be part of a company in hypergrowth (+300% growth per month).<br>Take on big technical challenges: <br>* Migration of the application to SwiftUI<br>* Creation of an internal SDK to manage the Design System: https://zeroheight.com/3a5051950/p/342813-introductionIf </p>\n<p>We have built 30% of the Build, we still have a long way to go! you want to explore our stack: https://stackshare.io/iziwork/iziwork</p>\n<p>Learning from others and sharing to others. Our team includes self-taught people, PhDs in computer science, mid-Senior and Senior developers, veterans who built several products from scratch. 💪<br> <br>In addition to a great start-up/scale-up experience: <br>- You'll be able to work in a pleasant work environment (our offices are in the 9th)<br>- Benefit from a very flexible remote/full remote policy! <br>- A custom career development/path: increasing process and performance reviews every 6 months<br>- Choice of 13\" or 16\" Macbook Pro<br>- Company events, afterworks... (remotely for now ;) )<br> </p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Qualifications</div>\n<p>- You have at least 2 years of experience as an iOS developer, with a minimum of Swift projects<br>- You master the iOS application design and development cycle up to publication on the store; ideally with at least one project completed independently and in its entirety<br>- Perfect knowledge of the iOS environment (SDK, OS, libraries, store...)<br>- Good knowledge of the app market and skills for UX/UI related topics<br>- You have good mental gymnastics (the path is more important than the goal). <br>- You like teamwork, and you also have the ability to take initiatives which allow you to dig into problems independently and share the findings. </p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Informations supplémentaires</div>\n<p><em>iziwork veille à développer un environnement de travail inclusif qui reflète la diversité dans ses équipes. Dans le cadre des procédures de recrutement, iziwork s’engage à être transparent et pertinent. En tant qu’employeur, iziwork offre à tous les mêmes opportunités d’accès à l’emploi sans distinction de genre, ethnicité, religion, orientation sexuelle, statut social, de handicap ou d’âge.</em></p>\n"
