        "description": "<p>Infopro Digital is one of the world’s leading B2B publishers in professional information and digital services companies, with 2,700 employees and over 50+ brands covering automobile, manufacturing and engineering, retail and e-commerce, insurance and finance, construction and architecture, tourism, and government authorities. An international presence which includes a vibrant culture and offices in Paris, London, New York and Hong Kong.We are a team defined by our people and passion, and a business powered by knowledge and innovation. We pride ourselves on our values, they define us and how we conduct ourselves both as a Company and as individuals. Our collaborative approach drives creativity. We believe excellent leadership creates an entrepreneurial environment that allows our people and brands to thrive. Everything we do is centered on trust, integrity, and respect.</p>\n<p>People are at the core of our company, helping us build market-leading brands and keeping us at the forefront of our markets. We recruit the smartest, encourage career progression and will give you all the support you need to help you succeed. Incisive people speak with authority and independence, are always curious and deliver the best products that our audiences trust and value.</p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>An exciting opening has arisen for experienced Drupal Developer on our software development team in London, but if you are located in Europe we will consider hiring you.</p>\n<p>You will be responsible for delivery of continuous improvements to our systems, that being websites, web applications, mobile applications as well as feeds, APIs and other bespoke systems.</p>\n<p>Developers have to make sure that all aspects of all our systems are operational, properly maintained and accessible to our end customers, that being our clients accessing the sites as well as internal users working on our content as well as external and internal systems consuming data and services provided by our systems.</p>\n<p>So, what makes our software team awesome?</p>\n<p>There are lots of opportunities to learn, grow and work on interesting projects. We are innovative and industry leaders using the latest technology (e.g. Drupal 8, Magento 2...) and products. We also offer our people the option of flexible and remote working!</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Self-starter with a proven record of own initiated projects delivering substantial ROI</li>\n<li>You must be driven, positive, resilient and personable</li>\n<li>Willing to learn, and to take on board new ideas and responsibilities</li>\n<li>Willing to use own initiative at all times</li>\n<li>Self-motivated, disciplined and hardworking</li>\n<li>Strong verbal and written communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"h3\">Must have</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Drupal (8+)</li>\n<li>PHP</li>\n<li>JavaScript, AJAX, JSON, jquery</li>\n<li>SQL – including MySQL &amp; PostgreSQL</li>\n<li>Latest HTML &amp; CSS</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"h3\">Should have</div>\n<ul>\n<li>NodeJS, React</li>\n<li>WordPress</li>\n<li>Python</li>\n<li>Git/SVN, Jenkins, Grunt/Gulp</li>\n<li>Linux, Apache, Nginx</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"h3\">Nice to have</div>\n<ul>\n<li>API design and integration</li>\n<li>Agile</li>\n<li>Test automation</li>\n<li>Technical documentation skills</li>\n<li>Google Analytics</li>\n<li>Solr / Lucene</li>\n<li>Worked using a ticketing system</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>We know great people make great companies. Infopro Digital is defined by people and passion, and powered by knowledge and innovation. Everything we do is centred on trust, integrity and respect. Our collaborative approach drives creativity across our markets; and our focus on giving teams ownership allows us to build an entrepreneurial culture where our people and brands can thrive and grow.</p>\n<p>We run a Foundation which supports a number of charities. Staff can volunteer to contribute their skills and expertise to make a meaningful difference to the lives of others.</p>\n<p>In addition to a competitive salary we offer the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>25 days annual leave (rising up to 30 days)</li>\n<li>Group personal pension plan</li>\n<li>Life assurance</li>\n<li>Interest free season ticket loan (STL)</li>\n<li>Private medical insurance</li>\n<li>Employee assistance programme</li>\n<li>Bonusly employee recognition</li>\n<li>Employee discount scheme</li>\n<li>Onsite monthly chair massage</li>\n<li>Eye-care Vouchers</li>\n<li>Discounted gym membership</li>\n<li>Agile/remote working</li>\n<li>Additional life assurance</li>\n<li>Bike to work</li>\n<li>Buying holiday</li>\n<li>Dental insurance</li>\n<li>Add partner to gym membership</li>\n<li>Health cash plan</li>\n</ul>\n"
