        "description": "<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Company Description</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Work for a Rapidly <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2021/03/29/testing-platform-tricentis-acquires-performance-testing-service-neotys/\" rel=\"nofollow\">growing</a>, pre IPO tech company, $200m revenue</li>\n<li>Global leader in DevOps, as recognized by <a href=\"https://devops.com/meet-the-winners-of-the-2020-devops-dozen%C2%B2-awards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">industry</a>, <a href=\"https://www.tricentis.com/blog/gartner-test-automation/\" rel=\"nofollow\">analysts</a> and our <a href=\"https://www.tricentis.com/news/tricentis-recognized-as-2020-gartner-peer-insights-customers-choice-for-software-test-automation/\" rel=\"nofollow\">customers</a></li>\n<li>Shape and grow our coolest new product in <a href=\"https://www.tricentis.com/news/next-gen-ai-powered-test-automation/\" rel=\"nofollow\">the artificial intelligence space</a>, Tricentis’ Vision AI</li>\n<li>Highly supportive of remote work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>About Tricentis</strong></p>\n<p>Tricentis makes the software industry’s #1 continuous testing platform and is recognized for reinventing software testing for DevOps. We aim to remain #1 by building the software testing platform of the future: AI-driven test automation, test management, change impact analysis, release readiness, performance engineering, operational continuity. Our mission is to empower every tester, developer, and decision-maker to deliver software with confidence and ease, making our customers wildly successful.</p>\n<p>We’re passionate creators – of products, of experiences and of the future of software testing automation.</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Job Description</div>\n<p><strong>About the Team</strong></p>\n<p>You will be working in the AI and Machine learning division. We build products and services that help make the rest of the organization faster. We work with cutting edge technology, custom neural networks and other machine learning to get the job done. Our team is highly independent, releases multiple times a week, and are all passionately committed to making our products the best they can be.  We are based in Sydney, New Zealand and Vienna.</p>\n<p><strong>About the Job</strong></p>\n<p>This is your job, described in a sentence: </p>\n<p><em>“Make sure our product continues to delight customers, and grows at an exponential rate”</em></p>\n<p>As a Product Manager in Tricentis, you will be expected to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lead our feature discovery efforts, building out our pipeline of customer priorities</li>\n<li>Define the product strategy and roadmap</li>\n<li>Determine Market-Product fit identify pathway to improving it</li>\n<li>Run beta and pilot programs with early-stage products and samples</li>\n<li>Be an expert with respect to the competition</li>\n<li>Act as a leader within the company</li>\n<li>Create a growth plan and gap strategy to take Vision AI to the next level</li>\n<li>Deliver customer and industry level seminars on the value of AI driven test automation</li>\n<li>Speak at customer and industry events</li>\n<li>Contribute actively and passionately to innovation initiatives and broader R&amp;D team spirit</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Qualifications</div>\n<p>This is what we are looking for in a Product Manager</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minimum of 5 years experience as a Product Manager or Product Marketing Manager</li>\n<li>Demonstrated success defining and launching excellent products (You must have at least 1 example in which you were the prime motivator)</li>\n<li>Experience in the Tech industry (driving technology based products such as SaaS products, installed components or other technology driven initiatives)</li>\n<li>Excellent written and verbal communication skills</li>\n<li>Bachelor’s degree, or equivalent industry experience</li>\n<li>Technical background, with experience in delivering SaaS products</li>\n<li>Excellent teamwork skills</li>\n<li>Proven ability to influence cross-functional teams without formal authority</li>\n<li>Ability to work with teams and customers across time zones</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"h3\">Additional Information</div>\n<p><strong>We offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Remote work done well and work-life balance.</li>\n<li>Interesting and fulfilling technical work.</li>\n<li>Career growth opportunities, with clearly defined targets and goals.</li>\n<li>The ability to work on open source tools.</li>\n<li>The technology you need to be productive.</li>\n<li>Team bonding and planning off-sites once travel is safe and reliable.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Tricentis is proud to be an equal opportunity workplace. Qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, national origin, sexual orientation, gender identity, disability or protected veteran.</p>\n"
